{"type": "article", "id": 18028, "title": "卡包", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-25T06:50:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021348168Pu9YTvpMLgz65kq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个卡包，打开磁扣能拉出有渐变颜色的卡包层，比通常的书页型的卡包更加清晰明了，彩虹一样的颜色让它显得很活泼，带来一种好心情。材料使用了专为工业生产使用的高性能织物，让它持久耐用兼具防水功能。此外，它的背后附有一个放零钱的小格。来自美国的团队 DAX 设计了这个卡包，有多种颜色搭配。<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/daxthewallet/dax-the-wallet-with-a-trick-up-its-sleeve\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134813YHhl52uTXC8noO1j.gif\" width=\"680\" height=\"453\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134814BHZeuwxorEcgCRW7.gif\" width=\"679\" height=\"453\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66715758\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134815erLsJuiAcya3pWX9.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134816xcNSLjWUZPflM7eB.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}